Yeah I read this website, and have been re-reading it every year or so, when
I think about doing some insulation on my bus. Finally I am getting to it. I
did not like the idea of fiberglass insulation, and only planned on putting
the great-stuff in areas that were inaccessible to any other types of
insulation. As he suggests-make sure no water needs to flow through an area
that you put this insulation. 
